    TransactionListener

    public static enum TransactionListener.PaymentEventType
extends java.lang.Enum<TransactionListener.PaymentEventType>
    The Payment Events we'll send to the app. These are currently a simple enum.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CardDataReceived
      The transaction manager has received card data.
      GettingPaymentInfo
      The transactionManager has entered a state of data collection.
      Idle
      The TransactionManager has entered the idle state.
      ProcessingPayment
      The TransactionManager has entered a state where it is communicating with the backend servers to collect a payment.
      TransactionCanceled
      The SDK has successfully canceled the payment with the backend.
      TransactionDeclined
      The EMV terminal declined the transaction and the SDK has successfully canceled the payment.
      WaitingForSignature
      The TransactionManager has entered a state where it has completed the transaction successfully and is waiting for the app to collect a signature from the customer and call the finalizePayment API.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • Idle

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType Idle
        The TransactionManager has entered the idle state. It is not doing any work and is ready to begin a payment or refund.

      • GettingPaymentInfo

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType GettingPaymentInfo
        The transactionManager has entered a state of data collection. beginPayment() has been called and we
        are currently collecting information from card readers or the application. You can now set a ShoppingCart, TransactionExtras, Signatures, and other data related to this payment.

      • CardDataReceived

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType CardDataReceived
        The transaction manager has received card data.

      • ProcessingPayment

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType ProcessingPayment
        The TransactionManager has entered a state where it is communicating with the backend servers to collect a payment. It is now too late to cancel the payment.

      • WaitingForSignature

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType WaitingForSignature
        The TransactionManager has entered a state where it has completed the transaction successfully and is waiting for the app to collect a signature from the customer and call the finalizePayment API.

      • TransactionCanceled

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType TransactionCanceled
        The SDK has successfully canceled the payment with the backend.

      • TransactionDeclined

        public static final TransactionListener.PaymentEventType TransactionDeclined
        The EMV terminal declined the transaction and the SDK has successfully canceled the payment.
